# Architecture Rules

Follow [`docs/architecture.md`](../../docs/architecture.md) and [`docs/adr.md`](../../docs/adr.md).

- Backend: Delivery → Application → Domain ← Infrastructure. Domain must not import Express, Mongoose, or R2 SDKs.
- Frontend: Pages → layouts → feature hooks/components → shared `components/`, `hooks/`, `services/`. No business rules in UI.
- Anonymity is enforced in API mappers and services — not only by hiding fields in React.
- ADR numbering: use [`docs/adr.md`](../../docs/adr.md) as the authoritative log.
